helm-pt
=====

A Helm interface for Pt, the [Platinum Searcher](https://github.com/monochromegane/the_platinum_searcher).

installation
============

helm-pt can be installed through [MELPA](http://melpa.milkbox.net/).

usage
=====

Working Directory - `M-x helm-do-pt` run pt from the current working directory in Emacs

Projectile - `M-x helm-projetile-pt` run pt from the `projectile-project-root` of the current project.  
